    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 premium executive sedan that perfectly balances athletic performance with refined luxury. The exterior is finished in a sophisticated Metallic Graphite that still holds a deep, mirror-like shine; while you may find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper from highway commuting, the body is remarkably straight and free of significant blemishes. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of Charcoal Dakota leather and brushed aluminum accents. The seats show minimal bolster wear, the carpets are pristine, and every electronic feature\u2014from the responsive touchscreen navigation to the panoramic sunroof\u2014operates exactly as intended. Under the hood, the turbocharged engine runs quietly and delivers power smoothly, backed by a comprehensive service history. We recently performed a full synthetic oil change and a multi-point inspection to ensure it is road-trip ready. This car has been garage-kept and smoke-free, offering a 'turn-key' experience for a discerning driver who appreciates a well-cared-for machine.",
